{
  "stem": "13524.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because who didn't get the working permit, it meant death.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I never did have the working permit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I did work occasionally, but never secured the permit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because we were told that you can only work from that age on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Up to certain age, you wouldn't qualify for work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we all had to carry a kennkarte with us, all had to have Ausweis to prove what age we are.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But occasionally, I managed to get on a truck-- because that's how we were collected-- to be taken to city to sweep the snow, or clean the German soldiers' barracks, or-- I remember once I went somewhere to clean the floors for a German officer to move in.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a lovely place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was a little pantry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in the corner, there was an onion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now that was really a reward for all scrubbing all the floors in that place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I came home, and I show my mother the onion I have found.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So my mother saw that I'm not as stupid as they thought.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They sort of allow me more often to go on those working excursions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And most of the time they were working excursion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Occasionally, you went on a truck, you didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
